# Task 4: Password Cracking Lab

## Overview
This folder documents the password cracking exercises performed using access
gained in Task 3. The /etc/shadow file was extracted from Metasploitable 2,
password hashes were saved to Kali Linux, and John the Ripper was used to
crack them. Cracked credentials were then validated via SSH login.

---

## Environment
| Component | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| Attacker | Kali Linux |
| Target | Metasploitable 2 — 192.168.56.101 |
| Tool | John the Ripper 1.9.0-Jumbo-1 |
| Hash Type | md5crypt ($1$) |
| Date | 8 May 2026 |

